zh_CN.DialogText: 我可不是什么铁石心肠的人...

en_US.DialogText: I'm not a hard hearted man

zh_CN.DialogText: 啊，这么说你愿意帮我了？

en_US.DialogText: Ah, so you're willing to help me?

zh_CN.DialogText: 就算你欠我一份大人情就好了

en_US.DialogText: Even if you owe me a big favor

zh_CN.DialogText: 不过你说在这种世界里，这么拼命求生真的值得吗？

en_US.DialogText: But do you think it's really worth living so hard in this doomsday world?

zh_CN.DialogText: 你怎么突然问出这么中二的问题？

en_US.DialogText: Why did you suddenly ask such a stupid question,like a chunibyo？
I really want to punch you
He laughed in spite ofhimself ‘ah, sorry’
Oh, sorry! I'll go back first!

zh_CN.DialogText: 嘿，你还没告诉我，你小子住在哪里啊

en_US.DialogText: Hey, you haven't told me where your shed is

zh_CN.DialogText: 算了，我一会带你去他的小房间吧

en_US.DialogText: Forget it, I'll take you to his little room later

zh_CN.DialogText: 一会儿我自己去找吧，反正这里住的人也不多。

en_US.DialogText: I'll find it myself later. There aren't many people living here anyway.

zh_CN.DialogText: 或许这也就是为什么我们需要互相帮助的原因

en_US.DialogText: Maybe that's why we need to help each other
